** GET  /staff/employee

Returns page of Employee objects.

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/staff/employee

*** Parameters

| name          | description                                  | default   |
|---------------+----------------------------------------------+-----------|
| windowSize    | Specifies number of results on the page.     | 5         |
| currentPage   | Specifies the page of results to retrieve.   | 1         |
| filter        | Filter to limit result.                      |           |
| order         | Result's order property.                     | id        |

*** Headers

| name     | description                        | default           |
|----------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept   | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |

*** Example request

GET 
https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/staff/employee

**** Request

==

#+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
    GET /TrafficLiteServer/openapi/staff/employee HTTP/1.1
    Accept: application/xml
    Authorization: Basic *** Base64-encoded email:token ***
#+END_EXAMPLE

** GET  /job/{id}

Returns single Job object by id.

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job/{id}

*** Headers

| name     | description                        | default           |
|----------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept   | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |

*** Example request

GET  https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job/1

**** Request

==

#+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
    GET /TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job/1 HTTP/1.1
    Accept: application/xml
    Authorization: Basic *** Base64-encoded email:token ***
#+END_EXAMPLE

==

#+BEGIN_EXAMPLE

[[#top][top]]

** POST  /job

Updates job with submitted one and returns updated object.

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job

*** Headers

| name           | description                        | default           |
|----------------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept         | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |
| Content-type   | Specifies submitted data format.   | application/xml   |

*** Example request

POST  https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job

**** Request

==

#+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
    POST /TrafficLiteServer/openapi/job HTTP/1.1
    Accept: application/xml
    Content-type: application/xml
    Authorization: Basic *** Base64-encoded email:token ***
#+END_EXAMPLE

Returns single quote object by id.

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/quote/{id}

*** Headers

| name     | description                        | default           |
|----------+------------------------------------+-------------------|

** POST  /timeentries/batch

Updates page of sent time entries and returns page of their's updated
versions

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/timeentries/batch

*** Parameters

| name          | description                                                                                                                         | default   |
|---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------|
| forceUpdate   | Allow changes even when locked by approval flag is set or the task is complete. Also allows user to change lockedByApproval flag.   | false     |

*** Headers

| name           | description                        | default           |
|----------------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept         | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |
| Content-type   | Specifies submitted data format.   | application/xml   |

[[#top][top]]

** GET  /invoice/{id}

Returns single invoice object by id.

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/invoice/{id}

*** Headers

| name     | description                        | default           |
|----------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept   | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |

*** Example request

GET  https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/invoice/1

**** Request

==

#+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
    GET /TrafficLiteServer/openapi/invoice/1 HTTP/1.1
    Accept: application/xml
    Authorization: Basic *** Base64-encoded email:token ***
#+END_EXAMPLE

==

** GET  /order

Returns page of lightweight order objects.

*** Resource URL

https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/order

*** Parameters

| name          | description                                  | default   |
|---------------+----------------------------------------------+-----------|
| windowSize    | Specifies number of results on the page.     | 5         |
| currentPage   | Specifies the page of results to retrieve.   | 1         |
| filter        | Filter for list values.                      |           |
| order         | Result's order property.                     | id        |

*** Headers

| name     | description                        | default           |
|----------+------------------------------------+-------------------|
| Accept   | Specifies requested data format.   | application/xml   |

*** Example request

GET  https://sohnar-prod.apigee.net/TrafficLiteServer/openapi/order

==
